  "id": "endless-rizette",
  "name": "Endless Rizette",
  "title": "Maid of Midwinter",
  "description": "She didn't love Finn as soon as she saw him. That would be too much like a fairy tale. When he arrived beaten and broken from the attack on his village, Rizette nursed him the same way she would any new refugee. They called her the Angel of the Outer City precisely because she never turned anyone away.\n\nStill, she couldn't deny the kinship between them, both teenagers ripped from their families by the undead. When he had no place to go, it was only natural she invite him to live with her and her brother. How could she have known where it would lead?\n\nHow could she have known their growing love would lead to ruin?",
